          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"marimo-devparser\">marimo-dev.parser</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">All ast and regex machinery lives here. No other module imports ast.\nNo other module knows about marimo's notebook format.</span>\n</blockquote>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Three branches per AST node:</span>\n<ol>\n<li>ast.With (setup cell)  \u2192 Import, Const, Setup</li>\n<li>Decorated export       \u2192 Export</li>\n<li>Everything else        \u2192 skip</li>\n</ol></span>"
